title: What causes Obesity in Kiribati
summary: This chart indicates three possible Cause of Obesity in the Kiribati population .
It indicates the main Cause of Obesity was attributed to Genetic Cause with 40.1 percentage of the sample identifying that as the main reason .
Only 25 percentage indicated Fast_Food contributed to the problem .
gold: The causes of obesity in Kiribati are charted above to show that the predominant cause of obesity was found to be genetic at 40 % . Fast food was the lowest charted percentage at 24 % with lack of exercise only contributing 35 % towards the outcome .
